    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a living legacy. This isn't just a vehicle; it\u2019s a masterwork of engineering preserved as if the world stopped turning the moment it left the showroom floor. Every curve of its pristine silhouette tells a story of sun-drenched coastal drives and the quiet dignity of a machine that has been truly loved. To sit behind the wheel is to command a symphony of mechanical perfection, where the gentle hum of the engine whispers of adventures yet to come. It carries the soul of an era where craftsmanship was king, offering a driving experience so pure and evocative it feels like a secret shared between you and the open road. This is your invitation to own not just a car, but a timeless treasure that has been kept in a state of grace, waiting for its next great chapter.",
